Wait, `llvm.fabs` folded to `0x7FF0000000000000`. It didn't fold to poison. Let's check why.
In `SimplifyDemandedFPClass`:
```cpp
  if (const CallBase *CB = dyn_cast<CallBase>(VInst)) {
